node.text: @tay.mk Haha! Life will be bored without good food

Love shopping at Far east plaza but never get to try out the new station snack bar on the 5th level?

Now is time for you to try! Because they offer islandwide delivery during this period! Really 不要错过 hor!

A must to order their salted egg pork ribs! Request for more gravy to pair with rice. Super addictive I tell you! I even dip the omelette, prawn sauce chicken with it.. Give it a try, you wont disappoint 😋
